extendedInfo.description: City Same Day Couriers Driver AppCity Same Day Couriers drivers use this application to communicate with our dispatcher software.This App auto allocates available jobs to the nearest available drivers. Lets the system know when your available for work, going home and how much you have made for the day (money)Once downloaded, a username and password will be sent to the new driver to log on and start earning money with the number 1 same day courier company.
